'''[[Cannabis]] in [[Liberia]]''' is illegal.

==History==
During the [[First Liberian Civil War]], Charles Taylor raised funds for his fighters by selling cannabis from territories under [[National Patriotic Front of Liberia]] control.<ref name="Arnold2013">{{cite book|author=Guy Arnold|title=The International Drugs Trade|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=WHH1ON4EEXsC&pg=PA183|date=13 May 2013|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-135-45515-6|pages=183–}}</ref>

